<h3 id="installation">Installation</h3>

<p>Step 1. Download the file <a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jhvanderschee/jekyllcodex/gh-pages/_includes/carousel.html">carousel.html</a>
<br />Step 2. Save the file in the â€˜_includesâ€™ directory of your project
<br />Step 3. Add this to your layout:</p>

<pre><code>
  {% include carousel.html height="50" unit="%" duration="7" %}

</code></pre>
<p>Step 4. Create a YML file called â€˜carouselâ€™ in your data directory with this content:</p>

<pre><code>images: 
  - image: /uploads/slider/image1.jpg
  - image: /uploads/slider/image2.jpg
  - image: /uploads/slider/image3.jpg
  - image: /uploads/slider/image4.jpg
</code></pre>
